◉ 20 new birds to unlock.

◉ 3 exclusive birds to unlock at the bottom of the list, scroll down! Just download our other games to unlock these birds, very easy :)

◉ New layout for the bird shop.

◉ 3 new achievements.

◉ iAd ads removed on the iPad.

Reminder : The new Park Mode is now available! Improve your park to see more birds flying around! Collect diamonds falling down from the birds when you tap on them.

If you like the game and want to support us, please write or update your review on the AppStore! Thank you very much.

Check out all our amazing games, search for the word "ketchapp" in the AppStore's search field.
